OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers are likely in the east this
OL,7,Fevening, which could be heavy and
OL,8,Fthundery. Otherwise it looks mainly
OL,9,Fdry with late sunshine giving way to
OL,10,Fsome clear spells overnight. Some low
OL,11,Fcloud and fog patches developing in
OL,12,Fthe west.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FSome very warm to hot hazy
OL,15,Fsunshine. However, misty low cloud in
OL,16,Fthe far west for a while, and a few
OL,17,Fheavy, perhaps thundery showers
OL,18,Fbreaking out during the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
