OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWarm
OL,6,Fsunshine and just a small chance of a
OL,7,Fheavy, thundery shower on Friday and
OL,8,FSaturday. Turning cooler by Sunday,
OL,9,Fwith showery, breezy weather arriving
OL,10,Ffrom the west.
